  <div class="card-header">
    Suggestion
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <h5 class="card-title">Create goals to get achivements</h5>
    <p class="card-text"><a href="/newGoal" class="text-primary"style="text-decoration:none;">Sure is quiet here! why don't you create a goal for this {{todays_date}}, {{day_name}}? </a></p>
